# Summary

cmdOS Desktop Agent represents the transition from application-based computing to intent-based computing.

Traditional systems require users to operate applications.

cmdOS allows users to express goals and enables AI Agents to execute tasks across the desktop environment.

The Desktop Agent becomes the bridge between human intent and real-world computer execution.
